snippet.title: *** Apology Video *** Johnny Depp and Amber Heard release apology video
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard release Pistol and Boo apology video, Barnaby Joyce says it reinforces laws

Deputy Prime Minister Barnaby Joyce says he hopes a video released by Hollywood star Johnny Depp and his wife reinforces that Australia's biosecurity laws are not "a joke".

Mr Joyce has shared the pro-quarantine video on his Facebook page, following Amber Heard's court appearance in Queensland.
